1
00:00:00,479 --> 00:00:07,580
The ceiling of the house in the shape of a cone,

2
00:00:07,580 --> 00:00:11,968
Would talk some more, tongue seems of stone

3
00:00:11,968 --> 00:00:33,112
Air a tad thick, too slow, too cold

4
00:00:33,112 --> 00:00:36,781
Up against the ribs, seems to fit the mold.

5
00:00:36,781 --> 00:00:40,451
Such things never really have a name

6
00:00:40,451 --> 00:00:44,201
Tuesday morning, all same - such a shame.

7
00:00:44,201 --> 00:00:46,994
Better get up before the alarm

8
00:00:46,994 --> 00:00:48,829
Perfer to stay under covers,

9
00:00:48,829 --> 00:00:51,271
next to you, cozy and warm

10
00:00:51,621 --> 00:00:54,893
Ah great, translucent little fate

11
00:00:54,893 --> 00:00:59,281
suddenly solid enought to carry such weight.

12
00:00:59,281 --> 00:01:02,951
The clock on the wall has no hands, just a face

13
00:01:02,951 --> 00:01:06,989
Many things here so out of place.

14
00:01:07,340 --> 00:01:11,329
Aye, geometry all wrong

15
00:01:11,329 --> 00:01:14,281
angles sharp, sides too long

16
00:01:14,281 --> 00:01:17,394
mirror mirror, warped in the glass

17
00:01:17,394 --> 00:01:21,144
Watching the present turn into the past

18
00:01:21,144 --> 00:01:24,813
come into focus, sharp and real

19
00:01:24,813 --> 00:01:27,766
accepting the lot, your given deal.

20
00:01:27,766 --> 00:01:31,995
little dear in the headlight

21
00:01:31,995 --> 00:01:40,661
was this all to bright?

22
00:01:41,010 --> 00:01:44,760
smooth brittle texture, gradient rough

23
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:48,031
maps of a depth worn out tough.

24
00:01:48,031 --> 00:01:51,462
trembeling splatter torn at the seem

25
00:01:51,462 --> 00:01:54,653
gausian blur of this in-between.

26
00:01:54,653 --> 00:01:58,004
I cant make you out, there in the back

27
00:01:58,004 --> 00:02:02,153
cut me some corners or cut me some slack.

28
00:02:02,153 --> 00:02:06,382
or at the very least show me your face,

29
00:02:06,382 --> 00:02:09,862
tell me you left me a singular trace.

30
00:02:10,212 --> 00:02:11,729
breath are small ghosts

31
00:02:11,729 --> 00:02:13,962
that leave the room,

32
00:02:13,962 --> 00:02:17,712
unhesitating, part into fume.

33
00:02:17,712 --> 00:02:21,223
Bless you, not only when you sneeze.

34
00:02:21,223 --> 00:02:24,145
But so you can them gently appease.

35
00:02:24,495 --> 00:02:30,558
Yup, geometry still strange

36
00:02:30,558 --> 00:02:33,590
tune the function to rearrange

37
00:02:33,590 --> 00:02:36,383
the flux of a beating heart

38
00:02:36,383 --> 00:02:40,532
the ordinary wonderful part

39
00:02:40,532 --> 00:02:44,282
open your eyes, its here, this deal

40
00:02:44,282 --> 00:02:47,633
accepting the lot, accepting what's real

41
00:02:47,633 --> 00:02:51,383
little dear in the headlight

42
00:02:51,383 --> 00:02:52,788
was this all to bright?

43
00:02:53,138 --> 00:02:56,649
few steps to the door

44
00:02:56,649 --> 00:03:00,638
few theps to the porch

45
00:03:00,638 --> 00:03:03,989
Lit by a singular burning torch

46
00:03:03,989 --> 00:03:07,340
could you just come and get some rest

47
00:03:07,340 --> 00:03:11,250
Swear I am not putting you to the test

48
00:03:11,250 --> 00:03:17,153
pacing, bracing yourself for the worst.

49
00:03:17,153 --> 00:03:53,506
wont be the last, wasnt the first.

50
00:03:53,855 --> 00:03:58,085
clear all clear

51
00:03:58,085 --> 00:04:01,596
off you go

52
00:04:01,596 --> 00:04:05,664
i'll se you later yeah,

53
00:04:05,664 --> 00:04:10,472
when your back or so.---

54
00:04:10,451 --> 00:04:14,681
no more time now for chitchat

55
00:04:14,681 --> 00:04:18,350
but sooner or later,

56
00:04:18,350 --> 00:04:22,120
yes.. sweetheart---

57
00:04:22,100 --> 00:04:25,692
I promise you that.
